      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ENGLISH DANCE (5) finished tenth last start over 2200m at this track, after a good third here the run prior. Beautifully placed and is sure to play a major role. LOYOLA TRIOS (3) won at this circuit two runs ago but couldn't repeat the dose at his latest appearance over 2200m at this venue, beaten 6 metres. Sure to enjoy an economical run from this draw. Meets a comparable field and he can get the job done. ROCK AMOUR (10) was out of the money two runs ago then broke and finished seventh last start over 1609m at Hobart, coming home 15 metres from the winner. Hard to know where he gets from this slightly awkward draw but rates a live chance in a similar assignment. REMEMBER ME NOW NZ (4) last appeared when fifth over 1609m at Hobart 14 months ago. Must be respected while fresh.",
